  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Also at 6th level, you learn a new and unique efficient molding technique called the <strong>Charged Blade Technique</strong>. When you cast a bukijutsu with the ninjutsu keyword or using your Imbued Weapon as a component, you can embolden the jutsu you cast. You can use this molding in addition to any other moldings you are using and has an Alternate Cost of 5.</p><p>The bukijutsu now deals force damage or whatever damage type your Imbued Weapon deals. The jutsu gains the Ninjutsu keyword if it didn't have it already, and its attacks gain a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls for every 5 chakra spent to cast the jutsu, up to a maximum of +5.</p>",
